Certain events should only happen once.

Examples:

Opening tutorial
First Rocket
First Bomb
First Thunder
First Obstacle
First Story Choice
First Daily Reward

The responsible system emits a SignalBus event.

SaveManager records the completion and saves the updated progress.

Future replays skip them automatically.

